#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate\\_normal"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:1 of
msgid "Draw random samples from a multivariate normal distribution."
msgstr "从多变量正态分布中抽取随机样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:3 of
msgid ""
"The multivariate normal, multinormal or Gaussian distribution is a "
"generalization of the one-dimensional normal distribution to higher "
"dimensions.  Such a distribution is specified by its mean and covariance "
"matrix.  These parameters are analogous to the mean (average or "
"\"center\") and variance (standard deviation, or \"width,\" squared) of "
"the one-dimensional normal distribution."
msgstr ""
"多变量正态分布（也称为多元正态分布或高斯分布）是一维正态分布向高维的推广"
"。这种分布由其均值和协方差矩阵指定。这些参数类似于一维正态分布的均值（"
"平均值或“中心”）和方差（标准差，或“宽度”的平方）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:10 of
msgid "Mean of the N-dimensional distribution."
msgstr "N维分布的均值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:12 of
msgid ""
"Covariance matrix of the distribution. It must be symmetric and positive-"
"semidefinite for proper sampling."
msgstr "分布的协方差矩阵。为了正确采样，它必须是对称且半正定的。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:15 of
msgid ""
"Given a shape of, for example, ``(m,n,k)``, ``m*n*k`` samples are "
"generated, and packed in an `m`-by-`n`-by-`k` arrangement.  Because each "
"sample is `N`-dimensional, the output shape is ``(m,n,k,N)``. If no shape"
" is specified, a single (`N`-D) sample is returned."
msgstr ""
"例如，给定形状 ``(m,n,k)``，将生成 ``m*n*k`` 个样本，并排列成 `m` 行 `n` "
"列 `k` 层的形式。由于每个样本是 `N` 维的，输出形状为 ``(m,n,k,N)``。如果"
"未指定形状，则返回一个 (`N` 维) 样本。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:20 of
msgid "Behavior when the covariance matrix is not positive semidefinite."
msgstr "当协方差矩阵不是半正定时的行为。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:22 of
msgid "Tolerance when checking the singular values in covariance matrix."
msgstr "检查协方差矩阵中的奇异值时的容差。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:24 of
msgid "Desired chunk size on each dimension"
msgstr "每个维度上期望的分块大小"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:26 of
msgid "Allocate the tensor on GPU if True, False as default"
msgstr "如果为 True，则在 GPU 上分配张量，默认为 False"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:28 of
msgid "Data-type of the returned tensor."
msgstr "返回张量的数据类型。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:31 of
msgid ""
"**out** -- The drawn samples, of shape *size*, if that was provided.  If "
"not, the shape is ``(N,)``.  In other words, each entry "
"``out[i,j,...,:]`` is an N-dimensional value drawn from the distribution."
msgstr ""
"**out** -- 抽取的样本，形状为 *size*（如果提供了该参数）。否则形状为 ``(N"
",)``。换句话说，每个条目 ``out[i,j,...,:]`` 是一个从该分布中抽取的 N 维值"
"。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:31 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"**out** -- The drawn samples, of shape *size*, if that was provided.  If "
"not, the shape is ``(N,)``."
