#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:39 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:40 of
msgid ""
"The mean is a coordinate in N-dimensional space, which represents the "
"location where samples are most likely to be generated.  This is "
"analogous to the peak of the bell curve for the one-dimensional or "
"univariate normal distribution."
msgstr ""
"均值是 N 维空间中的一个坐标，表示样本最可能被生成的位置。这类似于一维或单"
"变量正态分布的钟形曲线的峰值。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:45 of
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Covariance indicates the level to which two variables vary together. From"
" the multivariate normal distribution, we draw N-dimensional samples, "
":math:`X = [x_1, x_2, ... x_N]`.  The covariance matrix element "
":math:`C_{ij}` is the covariance of :math:`x_i` and :math:`x_j`. The "
"element :math:`C_{ii}` is the variance of :math:`x_i` (i.e. its "
"\"spread\")."
msgstr ""
"协方差表示两个变量共同变化的程度。从多变量正态分布中，我们抽取 N 维样本 :"
"math:`X = [x_1, x_2, ... x_N]`。协方差矩阵元素 :math:`C_{ij}` 是 :math:`x"
"_i` 和 :math:`x_j` 的协方差。元素 :math:`C_{ii}` 是 :math:`x_i` 的方差（"
"即其“散布”程度）。"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:52 of
msgid ""
"Instead of specifying the full covariance matrix, popular approximations "
"include:"
msgstr "除了指定完整的协方差矩阵，常用的近似包括："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:55 of
msgid "Spherical covariance (`cov` is a multiple of the identity matrix)"
msgstr "球面协方差（`cov` 是单位矩阵的倍数）"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:56 of
msgid ""
"Diagonal covariance (`cov` has non-negative elements, and only on the "
"diagonal)"
msgstr "对角协方差（`cov` 只在对角线上有非负元素）"

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:59 of
msgid ""
"This geometrical property can be seen in two dimensions by plotting "
"generated data-points:"
msgstr "这个几何特性可以通过绘制生成的数据点在二维空间中观察到："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:65 of
msgid "Diagonal covariance means that points are oriented along x or y-axis:"
msgstr "对角协方差意味着点沿着 x 轴或 y 轴方向排列："

#: maxframe.tensor.random.multivariate_normal.multivariate_normal:74 of
msgid ""
"Note that the covariance matrix must be positive semidefinite (a.k.a. "
"nonnegative-definite). Otherwise, the behavior of this method is "
"undefined and backwards compatibility is not guaranteed."
msgstr ""
"请注意，协方差矩阵必须是半正定的（也称为非负定）。否则，此方法的行为是"
"未定义的，并且不保证向后兼容性。"

